dc_title_s: Carta del corridoio Bizantino : la toponomastica e i confini
dc_description_s: Remote-sensing map overlayed with information showing the Byzantine Corridor; survey of toponyms origins; probable battle fields; historical sites; and Flaminia, Amerina, and Orvietana vias . At head of title: "Regione dell'Umbria, area Assetto del territorio - PUT." "Tavola II." Original map is filed with companion volume in Firestone Library, call number: DG975.U5 C677 1999
dc_publisher_s: Spoleto : Centro italiano di studi sull'alto Medioevo, 1999.
